<p class="titlebold">CHANGING THE APPEARANCE OF AN ORDER SITE</p>
<p class="text">There are three categories of changes
    that can be made to an order site's appearance: General, Top Bar &amp; Menu
  and Advanced.</p>
<p class="text"><strong>GENERAL<br>
</strong>General appearance settings include Site Title, Page Background 
Color, Page Background Image and font styles for content pages.</p>
<p class="text"><strong>TOP BAR &amp; MENU<br>
</strong>This section contains settings for the banner color, banner 
  graphic, menu color and font styles. Two custom links may also be added to the 
site's menu.</p>
<p class="text"><strong>ADVANCED<br>
</strong>The advanced appearance settings allow custom font styles 
for different categories of text that will appear on an order site.</p>
<p class="text"><strong>SEE ALSO:</strong></p>
<p class="text"><strong><span class="text"><a href="site-settings.php"></a></span></strong><a href="site-settings.php">Changing settings for an order 
  site</a></p>
